Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:53.51,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使告訴我你的勇氣　即使逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:58.31,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一個人便無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:02.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一日的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:07.78,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於我心深處　只步未移
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:12.69,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:18.48,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為不能忘記 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:23.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
