Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啊 Agristor等離子場的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我留下機體消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這庫爾吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…Gun…dam…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…Gun…dam…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…Gun…dam…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,……Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 Exia的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣是Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機體是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Throne 三號機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne Drei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一號機和二號機由哥哥們駕駛著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這時候一定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機 注意保持隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣把Gundam帶回總部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責指揮的可是 帕特利庫·克拉薩瓦 本大爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 只要得到Gundam 大佐的想法一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 Hellion部隊 確認大損
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員注意保持警惕 帶翅膀的說不定何時會暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架Gundam攻擊了超人機關的設施 殺了我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這種壓迫感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這種運動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪個部隊搞砸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Throne 二號機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終結者 去吧 尖牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱 太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一擊要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯查德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這射程距離 可不是尋常兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還有別的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說過啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊形被攪得一團亂 暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個機體是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有資料 沒有資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我是趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne Eins的Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰·崔尼蒂?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兄妹們已經前往救助你的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊的任務已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
