Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從當前空域撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走啦 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒轍 真沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子最大範圍散佈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
