Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是尼娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個散佈範圍是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新的Gundam出現?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 受其增援影響 好像本隊的Gundam捕獲行動失敗了
